3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses a differentiable flow-to-depth layer and a depth fusion network, which are machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with a problem related to perception, which is a common area of research in AI. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with generating depth maps, which is a common problem in computer graphics.
